## Limitations

The findings presented are subject to several limitations. First, the data on gun-related incidents often lack comprehensive national databases, leading to potential gaps in the analysis. Additionally, the studies referenced may have varying methodologies and sample sizes, which can affect the generalizability of the results. Finally, cultural and regional differences in gun ownership and usage are not fully accounted for, which may influence the applicability of the findings to different populations.